		<td><b>Re: ROM that shows the colors</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can degauss the discolored TV using another (working) CRT. Face the screens together, line them up so that the centers are about even, and turn on the CRT. The degaussing coil in the working CRT will degauss both screens.<br /><br />Once may not be enough, so be sure to give the degaussing coil time to cool off between uses.<br /><br />And of course, you can use Kasumi's color test to see if the discoloration is gone. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_mrgreen.gif" alt=":mrgreen:" title="Mr. Green" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


