		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">JimDaBim wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">So, you think the TV itself is broken in some way?</div>Yep. From your description, it sounds like the shadow mask has become magnetized. The degaussing coil is supposed to demagnetize the shadow mask every time the TV turns on. Since the discoloration isn't going away by itself, the degaussing coil is probably not working.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
